{"tid":2032794,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴孔乙己","createTime":"2020-05-24T09:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T09:21:05.000Z","uid":160998,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9228a991ffd4fa8739a33a9f5e5bac7a026bd1f9","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"防暴警察一到店，所有街上行街的路人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「啊蛇，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「冰一袋，要幾枝凍水。」便拿出防暴槍。路人們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又犯偷竊罪了！」防暴睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我有天親眼見你偷了7仔的可樂，被斷正。」防暴便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「竊水不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊水！&hellip;&hellip;打完市民再補充糖份的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「再吵捉你強姦」，什麼「等陣有人會比返錢」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"7d1fa7743d460dd0f0651a24d0b8d41a4ad13337","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"啊蛇偷水唔算偷！補充體力必須架嘛！"},{"pid":"8d0b12109b32cd9c521b20ee436705990ba45c90","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"睇黎市民都可以學啊蛇咁補充左體力先"},{"pid":"e97bf24ef33ffb96da5fe4b4fffc480e8472167c","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"等陣pprb會幫啊蛇比返錢架啦"},{"pid":"c17526409427d5485ebadb863e5e425774d8ce45","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"421a83f6cd53da478fbd66c3a8d0654f32d9c462","tid":2032794,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"孔乙己因為偷嘢俾人打瘸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fe8f01cd81e6a1e5a88a16eb5ea846377f5b65","tid":2032794,"uid":38566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e97bf24ef33ffb96da5fe4b4fffc480e8472167c","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"等陣pprb會幫啊蛇比返錢架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"比咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事後比錢唔算偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00d5647a1a73dc6fc04beb625c5c7c348083639","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"421a83f6cd53da478fbd66c3a8d0654f32d9c462","tid":2032794,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"孔乙己因為偷嘢俾人打瘸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"再吵捉你強姦"},{"pid":"55947b6d134dba73c76985e67e7980722fbe5fa5","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"防暴喝過半碗酒，漲紅的臉色漸漸復了原，旁人便又問道，「毅進仔，你當眞認識字麼？」防暴看着問他的人，顯出不屑置辯的神氣。他們便接着說道，「你怎的連半條柴也撈不到呢？」防暴立刻顯出頹唐不安模樣，臉上籠上了一層灰色，嘴裏說些話；這回可是全是再吵捉你強姦之類，一些不懂了。在這時候，衆人也都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"7318ab4a5b9a2757afc3a667d00700caa77e6149","tid":2032794,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00d5647a1a73dc6fc04beb625c5c7c348083639","tid":2032794,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"421a83f6cd53da478fbd66c3a8d0654f32d9c462","tid":2032794,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"孔乙己因為偷嘢俾人打瘸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"再吵捉你強姦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/12oakfHMtEelbi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F12oakfHMtEelbi.gif&h=5a0e1953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXt03bT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXt03bT.gif&h=18eb35d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3Wy63G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai